articles.title: Zuckerberg vs Musk: X chief Elon leaks private messages with tech rival as he tells him to get serious over $1 - Daily Mail
articles.description: Zuckerberg and Musk appeared set to battle it out when the latter tweeted that he was 'up for a cage fight' with his fellow billionaire, who responded by saying: 'Send me location'.
articles.content:
Mark Zuckerberg told Elon Musk to get serious over their proposed $1billion super-fight or 'move on' in a string of messages leaked by his tech rival.
